<section xml:id="maxdb.installation" xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
 &reftitle.install;
 <para xml:id="maxdb.configure">
  By using the <option role="configure">--with-maxdb[=DIR]</option>
  configuration option you enable PHP to access MaxDB
  databases. <literal>[DIR]</literal> points to the directory
  that contains the installed MaxDB SQLDBC package.
 </para>
 <para>
  Windows users will need
  to enable <filename>php_maxdb.dll</filename> inside of &php.ini;.
 </para>
</section>

